{
  "stem": "2620.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The furniture, I don't remember about taking any of the furniture.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 151,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] No, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] But then we, you know, we still took-- whatever we took to the ghetto, we still took it along to that brick factory, because, you know, we thought that we didn't know where we are going.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But after that, everything was left.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 152,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They took everything away-- just what you had on you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I wore a suit, or maybe just a-- a sport coat and a-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 153,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's too far back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] Then we were-- we were boxed in-- the whole family, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- boxed cars-- and we still didn't know where we are going.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 154,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know until we arrived there, which was Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 155,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] How many people in the boxed car-- a lot of--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember, but it was-- it was packed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 156,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 157,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--filled up, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 158,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was probably something up at the top.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There may have been a window, or like, a screen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 159,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and children.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 160,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The SS.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 161,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 162,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well-- well, you saw, you know, you saw barracks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 163,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you saw-- you saw the barracks already.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know, my mother went with the women.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And luckily, my father, and my other brother, and I, we wind up together for a short time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, we-- we were together there in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But a short time after that, they made up a transport to go to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were still together, the three of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 164,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we were together in Warsaw, in the camp-- in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
